data.description: Location, location, location!  This 3-bedroom, 2-bath brick ranch style home is located close to the school. Boasting a wealth of desirable features including granite countertops, wood floors, spacious bedrooms, walk in shower, woodburning fireplace, covered back patio, spacious fenced backyard with storage building, and a convenient 2-car garage.
